{"type": "article", "id": 15984, "title": "折叠灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000334ek38NBvQVt6xGycL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款折叠灯，原本是一块 48 厘米宽的正方形不锈钢金属片，你可以顺着折痕折叠成想要的形状，再将灯泡包进去，所以每一款灯都是独一无二的并呈现出强烈的折纸感。光线通过折叠的灯罩放射出来，改变灯罩的开合意味着调整光线的明暗，完全体现了手工自由多变的特征。这是来自比利时的设计，一共有 6 种颜色选择，近期会在 Kickstarter 出售。<a href=\"http://folding-lamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> 这里是他们是主页。 </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143416HgUh3KflWqx90N6k.jpg\" width=\"560\" height=\"366\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65357143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143416UX3yz52ATQIwvNhm.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143417zFTZyhWwCKg74LqX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143417RMTHDvWXg1lUn04P.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}